.32041
[系統印表機-1]功能說明:

      o  將此報表檔由第一台系統印表機印出.

      o  第一台系統印表機就是 lp (PRINTER SPOOLER) DEFAULT DESTINATION.

      o  請由 UNIX 指令 lpstat 檢查 PRINTER SPOOLER 是否正常.

         ex: $ lpstat -t
             scheduler is running
             system default destination: pr1
             device for pr1: /dev/tty1a
             pr1 accepting requests since Dec  3 01:10
             printer accepting requests since Dec  1 13:19
             printer pr1 is idle.  enabled since Jan 19 10:33

.32042
[系統印表機-2]功能說明:

      o  將此報表檔由第二台系統印表機印出.

      o  第二台系統印表機由 shell script file - lp2 驅動

         lp2 內容如下 : lp -s -dpr2 $1

      o  請由 UNIX 指令 lpstat 檢查 PRINTER SPOOLER 是否正常.

         ex: $ lpstat -t
             scheduler is running
             system default destination: pr1
             device for pr1: /dev/tty1a
             device for pr2: /dev/tty2a
             pr1 accepting requests since Dec  3 01:10
             pr2 accepting requests since Dec  3 01:10
             printer accepting requests since Dec  1 13:19
             printer pr1 is idle.  enabled since Jan 19 10:33
             printer pr2 is idle.  enabled since Jan 19 10:33

.32043
 [終端機印表]功能說明:

      o  將此報表檔由接於終端機後的印表機印出.

      o  終端機後的印表機由 shell script file - p000 驅動

         p000 內容如下 : echo '\033[5i\c'
                         cat $1
                         echo '\033[4i\c'

.32044
 [畫面顯示]功能說明:

      o  將此報表檔顯示於終端機上,並可用指令翻前後頁或尋找字串.

      o  終端機顯示由 shell command : pg -n 驅動

      o  pg 指令: <space bar> <return> n+
                  n-
                  n<return>
                  l
                  /pattern
                  ?pattern
                  q


